click-plus-1: You have not added any reactions to the message
click-plus-2: Click + button above to configure selfroles.
role-hubs-desc: Let your members get roles by reacting to a message.
type-normal: Normal: Reacting adds roles, unreacting removes roles.
type-verify: Verify: Reacting adds roles, unreacting does nothing.
type-drop: Drop: Reacting removes roles, unreacting does nothing.
type-reverse: Reverse: Reacting removes roles, unreacting adds roles.
role-limit-desc: Limit how many roles you can get from this role hub.
role-limit-error: You cannot set a role limit in this mode.
connected-role: Role assigned if someone is on any voice channel
connect-role-desc: Let your members get roles by joining the channel.
type-ADD: Add: Add roles below without kicking.
type-REMOVE: Remove: Remove roles below without kicking.
type-TALK: Talk: Add role below for the time user is on the channel.
type-VERIFY: Verify: Add role below and kick user.
type-DROP: Drop: Remove role below and kick user.
type-TOOGLE: Toggle: Add or remove role below and kick user.
buttontype-normal: Normal: Clicking adds roles, re-clicking removes roles.
buttontype-verify: Verify: Clicking adds roles, re-clicking does nothing.
buttontype-drop: Drop: Clicking removes roles, re-clicking does nothing.
buttons-hubs-desc: Let your members get roles by clicking buttons below message.
select-hubs-desc: Let your members get roles by selecting options below message.
